<div class="cover-page">

  <h1>PARTICULARS OF CLAIM</h1>

  <h2>NIKODEM KLASIK v PLATZKI LTD</h2>

 

  <div class="case-info">

    <p>

      <strong>Claimant (in person):</strong> Nikodem Klasik

    </p>

    <p>

      <strong>Respondent:</strong> Platzki Ltd, 229 Deansgate, Manchester, M1 4JQ

    </p>

    <p>

      <strong>Tribunal:</strong> Employment Tribunal (North West) - Manchester

    </p>

    <p>

      <strong>Case Number:</strong> [To be assigned by Tribunal]

    </p>

  </div>

 

  <p style="margin: 50pt 0pt 20pt 0pt; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6;">

    <strong>Claims Presented:</strong>

  </p>

 

  <ul style="text-align: left; display: inline-block;">

    <li>Unfair Dismissal (ERA 1996 s.98(4); s.104)</li>

    <li>Disability Discrimination (EqA 2010 s.15, s.20-21)</li>

    <li>Harassment (EqA 2010 s.26)</li>

    <li>Unlawful Deduction of Wages (ERA 1996 s.13)</li>

    <li>Additional Hours / Unpaid Overtime (ERA s.13; Contract)</li>

    <li>Breach of Contract (Express &amp; Implied Terms)</li>

    <li>ACAS Code Breach (Procedural Unfairness - s.207A uplift trigger)</li>

  </ul>

 

  <p style="margin: 40pt 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: #666;">

    <strong>Date of Claim:</strong> 13 November 2025

    <br/>

    <strong>Prepared:</strong> 16 November 2025

  </p>

</div>

 

