    <br/>

    <strong>Legal Significance:</strong> EqA s.26 (Harassment - pressure during health crisis/vulnerable period); ERA s.13 coercion (implied deduction threat); Post-termination penalty (aggravated damages); Breach of goodwill.

  </div>

