<h1>A2: Additional Hours &amp; Overtime Work</h1>

 

<h2>A2.1 Scope Creep &amp; Operational Context</h2>

 

<p>

  While contracted as General Manager (GM), the Claimant's actual duties expanded beyond standard managerial role to include:

</p>

 

<ol>

  <li><strong>Floor cover:</strong> Shift work on the dining room / service floor when staff were reduced or absent.</li>

  <li><strong>Administrative burden:</strong> Centralised purchase authorisation (every transaction requiring manager sign-off); stock control reporting; system management.</li>

  <li><strong>Undocumented labour:</strong> Direction not to log time in the system, creating audit trail gap for hours worked.</li>

</ol>

 

<h2>A2.2 Evidence (Verbatim Quotes)</h2>

 

