    <br/>

    <strong>Significance:</strong> Public directive isolating Claimant from staff. Sent to entire staff group; effectively announces disciplinary process before Claimant formally notified. Intimidates staff from communicating with Claimant.

    <br/>

    <strong>Legal Significance:</strong> EqA s.26 (Harassment - isolation); Predetermination; Violation of dignity; ACAS Code §3 (communication standards).

  </div>

