<h2>A5.1 Pattern of Conduct (February - October 2025)</h2>

 

<p>

  <strong>Harassment claim based on cumulative conduct pattern:</strong> Nine-month pattern of dehumanising language, aggressive tone, isolation, and post-dismissal intimidation.

</p>

 

