  <li>Employer discriminated based on disability (ADHD) contrary to EqA 2010 s.15, s.20-21</li>

  <li>Employer harassed Claimant contrary to EqA 2010 s.26</li>

  <li>Employer breached implied term of mutual trust and confidence</li>

  <li>Employer threatened unlawful deductions contrary to ERA 1996 s.13</li>

